room_title: Escape room "Halloween Happening..." by Escapomania in Ocean City
room_address: 11805 Coastal Hwy Suite I Ocean City, MD 21842
room_description: Many moons ago - moons of all kinds - blood moons, giant moons, and moons to swoon the tides, a Witch arose from the depths of time. You don’t want to spend eternity as a servant to the Witch’s hand! Beware of the spooks and frights, only the brave will be able to find the antidote potion in short 45 minutes.
